- **Info Messages**: Blue notifications for general information

### 🚀 Performance Features
- **Responsive Design**: Proper form scaling and resizing
- **Fast Loading**: Optimized data binding and rendering
- **Smooth Animations**: Subtle visual transitions

## 📊 Data Visualization

### 📈 Grade Distribution
- ASCII bar charts with visual representation
- Percentage calculations with proper formatting
- Color-coded grade categories
- Professional statistical display

### 🏆 Rankings System
- Medal-based top performer display
- Detailed student information
- Professional ranking format
- Easy-to-read performance metrics

